SUMMARY:Community Art Show at Golden Belt Arts
DESCRIPTION:Art collectors and art lovers come out to the historic Golden Belt campus for our Annual Community Art Show. Over 100 local artists are part of one of our biggest events of the year. \nAround the corner from Hi-Wire Brewing Co. on the Golden Belt Campus. Show reception on Durham’s Third Friday (February 20) from 6pm-9pm.
