SUMMARY:Open Mic at West End Social
DESCRIPTION:It’s a weekly open-mic event hosted by The Most Open Mic held at West End Social\, offering five-minute slots for everything from stand‑up comedy to storytelling and even raw\, cathartic rants—often framed as “Monday Moans”. Also enjoy the weekly “Liquid Courage” drink special offering $7 margaritas.
