SUMMARY:Meditation + Yoga Flow with Recess Yoga
DESCRIPTION:If you’ve been running on auto-pilot lately\, this class is your pause. Join Diamond (she/her) for a 45-minute midday retreat of mind-body connection\, gentle yogic movement\, and a practice of meditation. This practice is located at Recess Yoga Durham. Please note the studio is accessible by stairs on the second floor. \nConnect with Diamond on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/carolinad1m3/ \nOver the past decade\, Diamond (she/her) has explored several paths of yoga\, leading to her completion of a 200-hour in-person Hatha/Raja Yoga & Meditation teacher training in Durham\, NC in 2024. Her training follows the lineages of Sri Dharma Mittra and Thich Nhat Hanh\, with a focus on mindfulness\, meditation\, and inclusivity.\nHer teaching style is gentle and empowering\, encouraging students to listen to their bodies\, honor their needs\, and explore the practice at their own pace. She believes yoga is a powerful tool for managing everyday stress and deepening self-awareness\, both on and off the mat. Off the mat\, Diamond works in hospitality as a restaurant manager in downtown Durham and enjoys exploring local food\, nature\, and live music. Whether you’re brand new or returning to the mat\, Diamond invites you to join her in a practice rooted in presence\, curiosity\, and self-discovery.
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/meditation-yoga-flow-with-recess-yoga/2026-03-10/
LOCATION:Recess Yoga Durham\, 345 W. Main st\, 2nd floor\, Durham\, NC\, Durham\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Fitness,Health
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_3056.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Recess Yoga Durham":MAILTO:admin@recessyogastudio.com
GEO:35.9965995;-78.9040012
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Recess Yoga Durham 345 W. Main st 2nd floor Durham NC Durham 27701;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=345 W. Main st\, 2nd floor\, Durham\, NC:geo:-78.9040012,35.9965995
END:VEVENT
