SUMMARY:Silver Clay Jewelry Making
DESCRIPTION:Discover the magic of silver clay! In this beginner-friendly class\, you’ll create a pendant using silver clay. Learn to shape\, refine\, and texture your design before we kiln fire it. You’ll finish by polishing your piece and attaching findings\, leaving with ready-to-wear 99.9% fine silver jewelry.
