SUMMARY:Pony Ride with Ponysaurus Brewing Co.
DESCRIPTION:The Pony Ride is a social\, leisure bike ride that begins at 6:30pm at The Bull in CCB Plaza in Downtown Durham (201 Corcoran St\, Durham\, NC 27701). Gather at 6:30pm at the Bull in downtown Durham. Ride should be rolling out by 7pm and will end at Ponysaurus Brewing Co. Route will take about 1 hour. Ride distance: 5-8 miles (leisurely pace). \nEnter for a chance to win beer prizes – get your free raffle ticket at the Bull before the ride and be present at Ponysaurus at the end of the ride to win. Limit one ticket per participant. \nThe goal of The Pony Ride is to raise awareness of cycling and cyclists on the road in Durham\, foster the cycling community and provide a fun easygoing social environment for people to come together\, ride bikes and enjoy great beers\, good food\, and Downtown Durham. Celebrate the awesome city we live in\, the great people that live here\, and the joy we all get from getting outside and riding bikes! This is a social ride\, and riders of all levels are welcome!
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/pony-ride-with-ponysaurus-brewing-co-2/2026-03-10/
LOCATION:Ponysaurus Brewing Co.\, 219 Hood Street\, Durham\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Bicycling,Brewery,Sports
