SUMMARY:Better Together: An Evening of Storytelling with Jubilee Home
DESCRIPTION:“Better Together” is an evening of storytelling and reflection centered on this year’s theme of healing and connection. Through powerful personal stories and shared moments of reflection\, the event brings together residents\, partners\, supporters\, and friends of Jubilee Home to celebrate the relationships that make this work possible and the lives transformed when housing\, dignity\, and belonging come first. In a time when fear and division too often shape our public life\, “Better Together” offers space to pause\, reconnect and be renewed by one another.
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/better-together-an-evening-of-storytelling-with-jubilee-home/
