DESCRIPTION:Test your music knowledge against other Jug drinkers on the 2nd and 4th Tuesdays every month. Bring a team of your most diverse music-loving friends to win! Host Ash will have five rounds for you to prove your skills and win prizes. So grab a drink and see if you can come out on top!. \nHappens on the following Dates:\nJan 13\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nJan 27\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nFeb 10\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nFeb 24\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nMar 10\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nMar 24\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nApr 14\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nApr 28\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nMay 12\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nMay 26\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nJun 9\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nJun 23\, 2026\, 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)
