DESCRIPTION:Learn the basics of glass fusing and create a 3.5×3.5 inch square that will be turned into a coaster / trinket dish / night light. There will be a variety of colors of glass to choose from to design your own unique piece of art. \nGlass pieces will be fired after class and ready for pick up approximately one week after class. You will be contacted to arrange pick up.
