SUMMARY:Pappy & Fitz: Whiskey Tasting Supporting Siembra NC
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special whiskey tasting at Motorco x Parts & Labor that brings great pours and a great cause together. At $50 per ticket\, you’ll get to enjoy either: a 1.5 oz pour of 10-Year Pappy Van Winkle Kentucky Straight Bourbon or a 1.5 oz pour of 19-Year Old Fitzgerald Bottled-in-Bond Bourbon\, a rare opportunity to taste two iconic whiskeys side by side. \nWe’re excited to welcome Will Ball from Sazerac\, who will lead the tasting and share some insight into each pour’s history\, flavor\, and craftsmanship. Plus\, $15 from every ticket sold will be donated to Siembra NC\, so your night out directly supports a local organization doing meaningful work in our community. \nAdditional pours of Buffalo Trace\, Eagle Rare\, and a few other fantastic whiskeys will be available à la carte\, with the Parts & Labor kitchen offering a couple whiskey-friendly food specials designed to complement your tasting. Whether you’re a seasoned bourbon lover or just looking for a memorable night out for a good cause\, this is a tasting you won’t want to miss. Cheers to good whiskey and giving back!
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/pappy-fitz-whiskey-tasting-supporting-siembra-nc/
LOCATION:Motorco\, 723 Rigsbee\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adults Only,Wines, Spirits, Beer and Cheer
