SUMMARY:Pony Run at Ponysaurus Brewing Co. with Fleet Feet Raleigh & Morrisville
DESCRIPTION:Beer and running\, a pairing as old as time! Join the good people of Fleet Feet Carrboro & Durham at Ponysaurus Brewing Co. every Thursday for a 3-mile route or 5-mile route. Expect a good time and treat yourself to a pint at the end of every run for a job well done! \nArrive at Ponysaurus Brewing Co. at 6:15pm to check-in\, announcements and run at 6:30pm. The run is free and all levels/speeds are welcome.
