SUMMARY:Durham History Trivia with the MoDH and Bull City Discovery Society
DESCRIPTION:Join us in person for an awesome night of Durham history trivia hosted by the Museum of Durham History (MoDH) and the Bull City Discovery Society. Meet fellow history buffs\, learn cool local facts\, and show off what you know about Durham’s past. Don’t miss out on this exciting chance to dive into Bull City’s rich stories while having a blast! Plus the top 3 winners of each round will receive Museum of Durham History swag bags!
